originalText.text: I was fortunate a Google search led me to Gigi. When I read her profile a few things resonated, so I went with my instincts and hired her for coaching. Fast forward two years and my life is so much happier and more rewarding, and I’m so thankful for the tools Gigi gave me to help me move forward and trust in myself and my future again. I love that she’s followed up a few times since and really look forward to meeting her in person at some point soon!

originalText.text: Gigi has helped me greatly in looking at my life from a new perspective. I have been feeling quite depressed over some decisions I made in the past that affected the entire trajectory of my life, and many times I wish I had made different decisions than those that I did make so many years ago. Gigi helped me realize that the decisions I made then were made for a good reason at that time and served their purpose. That was then and this is now. Gigi let me see that I am now free to change the trajectory of my life to a path that is more fulfilling for me! I feel much more positive about what the future holds for me! Thank you, Gigi.

originalText.text:
I recently visited Dr. Arnaud's dental office and I was very pleased with their services.  The staff was courteous and welcoming, moving at an office suite was cozy and clean, and made me feel relaxed and nerve-free, which is unusual for me when i visit the dentist.  The Doctor was just so pleasant. She was friendly, professional, and made me feel very comfortable while she worked away at my teeth. Before i knew it, we were done, and she did a wonderful job. I would definitely recommend this office to anyone who wants a painless, worry-free dental experience, and i will definitely be coming back myself for regular oral checkups. Two thumbs up!

Sincerely,

Mona D.

Brooklyn
